{
  "stem": "1216.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They shaved, not their whole head, but a stripe in the middle.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And on the back of their uniform jacket, they painted a great big enormous red S for, again, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] and they had to do all the street cleaning and work and so on that we did.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We didn't-- in that sense, we were liberated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We were not liberated in the sense that we didn't get more food, because the Russians didn't have anything either.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we couldn't leave right away, for various reasons.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "A, there was a typhus epidemic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So typhus spreads very quickly, anyway.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There's no way they were going to let us out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "B, there was no transportation to be had.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So when, finally, the day came that the first ones could leave-- the Czechs were the first to go, because they were in their own country.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I have no idea whether they walked home, or how they got home, but at least they spoke the language.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "As far as my parents and I were concerned, we stayed-- we had to stay-- until about June 15 or so.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I wrote down June 20 on that questionnaire, that's not quite true.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I think it was about June 15.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Then, somehow, we got to Pilsen, well known for its beer, and there we were quartered for a week in what turned out to be the local insane asylum.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Sorry, but that's what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "That's what they were called at the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Where the mentally ill were pushed out of their rooms, essentially, into one half of the building, and we got the other half of the building.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Very nice, clean sheets, real beds, lovely, with the occasional food in between meals.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I don't remember any meals.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
